50|$|Following retirement, Sheldon {{remained}} {{active in}} <b>trade</b> <b>union</b> <b>affairs,</b> and chaired the Civil Service Appeals Panel. In 2005, Sheldon {{was invited to}} lead several independent internal trade unions investigations on behalf of PCS, the FBU and ASLEF.|$|E
